INSERT INTO `image_config` VALUES (1948282995874287617,'VOL.4674','摄影','http://wufazhuce.com/one/4822','时至今日，我都觉得察言观色与谨小慎微是一个小孩所能习得的最残忍的“美德”。','https://image.wufazhuce.com/FigL0pmIKEg5jv4HEtboJL67goLa','24 Jul 2025','2025-07-24 15:23:57',NULL),(1948282995895259137,'VOL.4673','摄影','http://wufazhuce.com/one/4821','理性的爱应该包括三点：先救自己、拥抱时间、不放弃希望。','https://image.wufazhuce.com/FrAcSB8yV_t5l6BfE_T0tcgKrUOR','23 Jul 2025','2025-07-24 15:23:56',NULL),(1948282995895259138,'VOL.4672','摄影','http://wufazhuce.com/one/4795','有时我们气喘吁吁地对自己说：“唉，生活就是赛跑。”其实，事实恰恰相反：生活是宁静的。一直在盲目奔跑的是我们。','https://image.wufazhuce.com/FskEOWb4tTwGzoF4H0HaG7NiSX3M','22 Jul 2025','2025-07-24 15:23:55',NULL),(1948282995895259139,'VOL.4671','摄影','http://wufazhuce.com/one/4820','爱，是为了自己的心，不是为了别人。','https://image.wufazhuce.com/FjjFRqNRz0Yi0wD-8MRHbXDRzgY3','21 Jul 2025','2025-07-24 15:23:54',NULL),(1948282995895259140,'VOL.4670','摄影','http://wufazhuce.com/one/4840','年轻人就这样被召唤着、驱使着，来到了世界的虚无当中。','https://image.wufazhuce.com/Fk7dhBwA9bL1amkw544F8vhgcn3t','20 Jul 2025','2025-07-24 15:23:53',NULL),(1948282995895259141,'VOL.4669','摄影','http://wufazhuce.com/one/4819','在这个世界上，每一个道理后边都包含着很多因素。可人们只说道理，不说“因素”。','https://image.wufazhuce.com/FvHXNi9yw3d-1_VKScxDBaDBqghT','19 Jul 2025','2025-07-24 15:23:52',NULL),(1948282995895259142,'VOL.4668','摄影','http://wufazhuce.com/one/4817','我不想自己生活在垃圾堆里。 我要在水流中找到细微的气泡，或制造气泡，让自己能够呼吸。','https://image.wufazhuce.com/Fv7sy6SjjvdcDY6Ww3Opur_TbqzA','18 Jul 2025','2025-07-24 15:23:51',NULL),(1948547594804547585,'VOL.4675','摄影','http://wufazhuce.com/one/4823','我真高兴。我有了爱，有了工作，有了钱，有了朋友，有了时间。','https://image.wufazhuce.com/Fms0xMNhYEZbi5ISuy3qDs1kpCf4','25 Jul 2025','2025-07-25 08:55:22',NULL);
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `image_config` ENABLE KEYS */;
